sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS Reencrypt
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS (service-ca)
    participant API as ds-pipeline-api-server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    participant S3 as S3 Object Store<br/>9000 or 443/TCP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow Controller
    participant Pod as Pipeline Pod<br/>(launcher/driver)
    participant MLMD as ds-pipeline-metadata-grpc<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant Envoy as MLMD Envoy<br/>9090/TCP gRPC
    participant MDRoute as MLMD Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: Pipeline Run Execution
    User->>Route: POST /apis/v2beta1/runs<br/>HTTPS/443
    Route->>Proxy: TLS Reencrypt
    Proxy->>Proxy: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(DSPA api subresource)
    Proxy->>API: Forward request<br/>HTTP 8888 (or HTTPS w/ PodToPodTLS)
    API->>DB: Store run metadata<br/>MySQL/3306, TLS (configurable)<br/>Auth: Password (Secret)
    DB-->>API: OK
    API->>S3: Store/retrieve artifacts<br/>HTTP(S)/9000 or 443<br/>Auth: AccessKey/SecretKey
    S3-->>API: Artifacts
    API->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    K8s-->>API: Created
    API-->>Proxy: Run created response
    Proxy-->>Route: Forward
    Route-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over Argo,S3: Flow 1 (continued): Pipeline Execution
    Argo->>K8s: Watch Workflow CRs<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    K8s-->>Argo: Workflow event
    Argo->>K8s: Create Pipeline Pod<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    Pod->>MLMD: Log execution/artifact lineage<br/>gRPC/8080, mTLS (PodToPodTLS)
    MLMD->>DB: Store lineage<br/>MySQL/3306, TLS
    Pod->>S3: Upload artifacts<br/>HTTP(S), AccessKey/SecretKey
    Pod->>API: Report status<br/>HTTP(S)/8888

    Note over User,DB: Flow 2: MLMD Lineage Query (Dashboard)
    User->>MDRoute: Query lineage<br/>HTTPS/443
    MDRoute->>Proxy: TLS Reencrypt
    Proxy->>Proxy: SubjectAccessReview
    Proxy->>Envoy: Forward<br/>HTTP/9090 (localhost)
    Envoy->>MLMD: gRPC request<br/>gRPC/8080, TLS (PodToPodTLS)
    MLMD->>DB: Query lineage data<br/>MySQL/3306, TLS
    DB-->>MLMD: Results
    MLMD-->>Envoy: gRPC response
    Envoy-->>Proxy: Response
    Proxy-->>MDRoute: Forward
    MDRoute-->>User: Lineage data

    Note over API,OCI: Flow 3: Managed Pipelines Import
    Note right of API: During DSPA reconciliation
    API->>OCI: Fetch managed-pipelines.json<br/>HTTPS/443, Registry auth
    OCI-->>API: Pipeline manifest
    API->>API: Validate pipeline names<br/>against manifest
    Note right of API: init-managed-pipelines extracts<br/>pipelines from OCI image layer<br/>into shared volume
    API->>API: Import pipelines from<br/>/config/managed-pipelines/
